old-fashioned gentleman.=E2=80=9D He liked to buy from dealers and at art f=
airs because =E2=80=9Che loved the interaction with people and didn=E2=80=
=99t mind the retail markup.=E2=80=9D Many fondly recall the dinners he arr=
anged annually during TEFAF Maastricht, as well as the dealers=E2=80=99 din=
ners he hosted every fall in his home. Indeed, among the very first items h=
e purchased were dining room pieces: a set of 18 Georgian carved mahogany
chairs ( https://www.sothebys.com/en/buy/auction/2025/the-vision-of-aso-o-t=
