om:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;">Beinecke worked closely with both=
 the Clark and
Sotheby=E2=80=99s to select the works that would be sent to each. =E2=80=9C=
We focused on making the right selections that would resonate with the whol=
e,=E2=80=9D she told me. =E2=80=9CThe Clark didn=E2=80=99t pick only the mo=
